### GET Available Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

###

### GET Shipments In Transit
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

###

### GET Shipments For Specific Customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq 'cust1'

###

### POST New Shipment Booking
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
  "customer_ID": "cust1",
  "driver_ID": "drv1",
  "vehicle_ID": "veh1",
  "pickupAddress": "Sector 62",
  "deliveryAddress": "MG Road",
  "pickupCity": "Noida",
  "deliveryCity": "Gurgaon",
  "weight": 120,
  "bookedAt": "2026-06-01T09:00:00Z",
  "estimatedDelivery": "2026-06-02T18:00:00Z",
  "actualDistance": 42,
  "charges": 1500
}

###

### PATCH Shipment Delivered
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments(<SHIPMENT_ID>)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Delivered",
  "deliveredAt": "2026-06-02T17:30:00Z"
}

###

### GET Routes Between Two Cities
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Delhi' and toCity eq 'Jaipur'

###

### GET Drivers Sorted By Rating Descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc